{"tid":699122,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【中国又贏】特朗普感謝習近平和韓日領袖對美朝峰會貢獻","createTime":"2018-06-12T09:05:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-12T09:31:15.000Z","uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b73b83552521e027dde2ba03b68bdf914267ea7a","tid":699122,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T09:05:13.000Z","msg":"特朗普感謝習近平和韓日領袖對美朝峰會貢獻<br />\n<br />\n2018-06-12 HKT 16:24<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1401294_1_L_20180612164553.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1401294_1_L_20180612164553.jpg&h=48a22ede&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n特朗普表示，希望過往的衝突，不會演變成明日的戰爭。（法新社）<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普與北韓領袖金正恩在新加坡結束歷史性峰會，並簽署聯合文件。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普之後在單獨舉行的記者會上說，峰會傳達了和平的訊息，又說與金正恩更了解對方，準備建立新的歷史，反映真正的改變，的確有可能發生。他希望過往的衝突，不會演變成明日的戰爭。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普感謝新加坡總理李顯龍及新加坡民眾，為峰會提供的協助。他又感謝南韓總統文在寅和日本首相安倍晉三，並特別感謝中國國家主席習近平對峰會的貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1401294-20180612.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1401294-20180612.htm&d=ZzA5IRrzd3BZ%2FN4D7BApPYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=130e5c17\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1401294-20180612.htm&h=8d06aa13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1401294-20180612.htm</a>"},{"pid":"f7d8e299ccdebaa9ddaa601021759d184c755763","tid":699122,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T09:06:51.000Z","msg":"所以放生中興<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f75078b5f04dd1a0d0f8bc183ac4f61d311d45db","tid":699122,"uid":10937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T09:31:15.000Z","msg":"是但啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>win win</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}